I don't know the options, but when depends on the method of loading. Is it
a monolithic driver (in the kernel, not a module)? Then use the append=
statement in lilo.conf. Else, if it's a module, then add it to the
/etc/conf.modules file on the ethernet line.
On Tue, 25 May 1999, Arni Raghu wrote:
