> 100MB).But I would like them to work as 10MB cards...
> 
> My kernel is 2.2.7(base RH 5.2)..I have compiled a non-monolithic kernel
> and have compiled the network drivers as modules with kerneld enabled
> and all that works just fine...
> 
> What are the options and at what time and how do I pass them to the
> kernel so that the cards work in 10 MB mode..??
